Introduction

LipBubble (Korean: 립버블) was a girl group under Zenith Media and debuted with "Popcorn" in 2017. Members consist of Ryua, Seoryn, Mirae, Haea, Eunbyeol, Ina. Hanbi, Seoryn, Ella, and Lia left the group in February 2019. Unfortunately, on May 20, 2019 LIPBUBBLE disbanded.
